{"tid":1391302,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"一名銀行從業員的心聲","createTime":"2019-07-31T11:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T03:31:18.000Z","uid":264887,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"748d1d50d67431c683c94d817b2a1cb4e333c8cc","tid":1391302,"uid":264887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"P牌仔，幫手轉發#ado<br />\n做金融嘅，希望聽日會見到你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qg8H0L7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQg8H0L7.jpg&h=3dc9d22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c4LOWjR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4LOWjR.jpg&h=979dec7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60a576a90827f2717f605a6a01a2ddd4fc20c8da","tid":1391302,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推，8月1號要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7c98db65a4f72178b657642f951c0eddf59f36","tid":1391302,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"1d2af92eb25c4389bec1b99dba85a364c97142dd","tid":1391302,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"無聽過咁濟，推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f80e5aaf50cbd3ec40ea5de24ca6767b8f161e","tid":1391302,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"得tg 有"},{"pid":"f9ddb189ebe4fc16da236343c103e1317520195e","tid":1391302,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"Push. 無人呀"},{"pid":"4441782d7e005fd89d9a324b354ea01ff2193c53","tid":1391302,"uid":51064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:32:13.000Z","msg":"推呀！！"},{"pid":"6e71e51e0676f3ddbf3c58519b8bbcaa83a47a75","tid":1391302,"uid":51064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:33:30.000Z","msg":"活動流程及注意事項<br />\n<br />\n1.請準時到達，逾時不候<br />\n2.當日天氣或不穩定，請自備雨傘(最好黃色/透明傘)<br />\n3.無dress code，著返返工衫is ok<br />\n4.到場後唔會有任何口號，盡量低調，好似默哀咁就得<br />\n5.活動開始時我會以電筒照向黃傘作為信號，其他人請陸續跟隨點燈，為令效果更好，請準備黃傘/透明傘<br />\n6.記住不交談，不暴力，不認識彼此<br />\n7.有popo趕就即散，不要作無謂爭論<br />\n8.活動將以和理非快閃方式進行，不設大台及代言人，但會有傳媒到場採訪及訪問參加者（必須得到受訪者同意）。<br />\n9.參加者自行衡量參與活動之風險，是次快閃並無申請不反對通知<br />\n10.現場為公眾地方，病菌容易傳播，可自己考慮佩戴口罩，預防交叉感染。<br />\n11.是次在遮打花園的活動不是公眾集會而是個人自發表達意見的形式。如果在警察在附近干預，或不允許市民進入會場，市民可各自可移至附近的皇后像廣場，開傘默立10分鐘，再慢慢用自己的方法走至IFC happy hour<br />\n<br />\n是次活動旨在喚醒一d唔敢出聲，又或者身邊比較多藍絲既同路人，俾佢地知道其實整個業界有好多人都同佢地有同一理念，都熱愛香港，呢條路唔係自己一個行，有好多人陪，同埋希望日後發起其他運動時有更多人加入"},{"pid":"16b27be311b4af5d26e656724e0f57d36727a1dd","tid":1391302,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:31:49.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350ce2a99b9e5f746884da77d08ca855ee725b2f","tid":1391302,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f986cf522512fd9f8993e598116345e9e14e35e0","tid":1391302,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"金融介人士！要人呀"},{"pid":"8dd319bf02c22e8a5c6bfc248d64d20e2635aa9f","tid":1391302,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ba47a667bd6555e2eaf629a71afb4ac0211794c","tid":1391302,"uid":292739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:50:28.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.g